Here is a PHP script that calculates and displays the sum of all odd numbers up to a given limit:

<?php

// Input limit
$limit = 10;

// Running total
$total = 0;

// Loop through all numbers up to the limit
for ($i = 1; $i <= $limit; $i++) {
    // Only consider odd numbers
    if ($i % 2 != 0) {
        // Add the odd number to the running total
        $total += $i;
    }
}

// Display the final sum
echo "The sum of all odd numbers up to {$limit} is {$total}.";

?>

